          "reviewBody": "Its good start for my kids to start their best education. Teachers here are so efficient to make kids learn things independently and build a interest on it. I'm grateful to Sai mam the phonics tutor for my kid. He is 5 years old and reads short story books , Sai mam has been patience with kids and her way for teaching never keeps child bored. A foundation is very important for everything to keep us best. Thank you Sangeetha mam and the all the teachers of Kridashala.",
