          },
          "reviewBody": "My child is in nursery, and I couldn't be happier with this school!\nThe staff is incredibly friendly and supportive, creating a warm environment for young learners.\nThey focus on developing a range of skills and encourage kids in sports, dance, and other activities from a young age.\nThey curate a weekly plan with such effort and dedication, it’s evident that the teachers genuinely care about the children's growth and well-being. A fantastic place for early education! Highly recommended!\n\nThey have inhouse app called kriyo it is very useful to keep track of school activities.",
          "publisher": {
